**2. Financial Performance Analysis**

**2.1. Revenue Growth**

Tesla's revenue growth over the past three years indicates its robust expansion. The following chart visualizes this growth:

```html
<div class="chart-container">
    <canvas id="revenueChart"></canvas>
</div>

<script>
